title: Information Employee Average Hourly Earnings, USA by State, January 2007-November 2008
name: Information Employee Average Hourly Earnings, USA by State, January 2007-November 2008
description: This dataset, from the US Bureau of Labor Statistics, is part of a larger dataset that provides "All Employee Hours and Earnings". This dataset gives the Information Employee Average Hourly Earnings per state for each month from January of 2007 to November of 2008. Not all states are included due to lack of data
